name: Moth Collection: Study N°2
description:
For me, moths bring together elements of beauty and darkness, lightness and obsession, softness and anxiety. They are  fairly harmless, but can destroy and eat apart. 

I had been collecting pictures of moths, so I sought more, and used those images as input for training AI, generating a body of  new moth images and combining those with my own style. 

Collect them, so they don't eat everything to pieces...
